page_0:
"Weitan,

You must be mad thinking of profit when the city is crumbling around us! If you really must get inside the palace, try the name of Caerul's First Emperor at the entrance. I have no idea how the treasury can be accessed, though. Some say you have to set another pattern of hieroglyphs at the entrance.
Even if you find the secret passage, its magical nature requires a particular way of navigating it, and the only person knowing how it works is sitting on his throne with a sword protruding from his forehead. 

Velan"
